We are the siblings behind iRock Your Party. We might look young to you, but we are all well seasoned in each of our event fields and make an awesome team. We have been involved in the industry for over 12 years and have always dreamed about combining our strengths and skills to create an entertainment company driven by passion, charisma, and attention to detail. SEBASTIAN Vision Director Whether on the decks, the mic, or the lights, he’s the mastermind behind unforgettable parties. When it’s time to rock, Sebastian sets the vibe and brings the vision to life. ​ Sebastian@irockyourparty.com ​ SANTIAGO Operations Manager Santiago, as our Director of Operations, keeps the finances sharp, the logistics smooth, and the team in sync, making sure every event runs seamlessly from start to finish. ​ Santiago@irockyourparty.com DANI Marketing Specialist & Designer Dani’s background in multimedia design and her photography expertise allow her to create dynamic visuals that capture the energy of our events. Whether designing, shooting, or editing, she makes sure iRock always looks as good as it feels. ​ Dani@irockyourparty.com ​ OUR ROCKSTAR TEAM DJS REY SEBASTIAN E2 LUIS BARR RAFAEL DARION SAMUEL JACOB MIKE OFFICE MANAGER WAREHOUSE & EVENT SUPERVISOR STEPHANIE JAVIER EVENT ASSISTANTS BIBIANNA DANIEL SEBASTIAN MATTEUS LENNY NOW THAT YOU'VE GOT TO KNOW US, ARE YOU READY TO ROCK WITH US?
